{
  "texts": [
    "The output format should look as follows: \"Feedback: (write a feedback for criteria) [RESULT] (Either \"A\" or \"B\")\" 5.",
    "Please do not generate any other opening, closing, and explanations.",
    "Instruction: {instruction} Response A: {response a} Response B: {response b} Score Rubrics: {rubrics} Feedback:",
    "The score rubrics in Table 3 mimic the original annotation guidelines, for humans in Summarize from Feedback and HelpSteer2 datasets, and GPT-4 in Nectar dataset.",
    "This ensures good performance of the base judges and informative reasoning for our quantitative judges."
  ]
}